{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I just want to say my name is Emmanuel Jal."},{"time":4000,"text":"And I come from a long way."},{"time":7000,"text":"I've been telling a story that has been so painful for me."},{"time":11000,"text":"It's been a tough journey for me, traveling the world,"},{"time":14000,"text":"telling my story in form of a book."},{"time":18000,"text":"And also telling it like now."},{"time":22000,"text":"And also, the easiest one was"},{"time":24000,"text":"when I was doing it in form of a music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26000,"text":"So I have branded myself as a war child."},{"time":32000,"text":"I'm doing this"},{"time":35000,"text":"because of an old lady in my village now,"},{"time":39000,"text":"who have lost her children."},{"time":42000,"text":"There is no newspaper to cover her pain,"},{"time":45000,"text":"and what she wants to change in this society."},{"time":48000,"text":"And I'm doing it for a young man"},{"time":51000,"text":"who want to create a change and has no way to project his voice"},{"time":55000,"text":"because he can't write."},{"time":57000,"text":"Or there is no Internet, like Facebook, MySpace,"},{"time":60000,"text":"YouTube, for them to talk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66000,"text":"Also one thing that kept me pushing this story,"},{"time":69000,"text":"this painful stories out, the dreams I have,"},{"time":73000,"text":"sometimes, is like the voices of the dead,"},{"time":77000,"text":"that I have seen"},{"time":80000,"text":"would tell me, \"Don't give up. Keep on going.\""},{"time":82000,"text":"Because sometime I feel like stopping and not doing it,"},{"time":85000,"text":"because I didn't know what I was putting myself into."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89000,"text":"Well I was born in the most difficult time,"},{"time":94000,"text":"when my country was at war."},{"time":97000,"text":"I saw my village burned down."},{"time":100000,"text":"The world that meant a lot to me, I saw it"},{"time":102000,"text":"vanish in my face."},{"time":106000,"text":"I saw my aunt in rape when I was only five."},{"time":110000,"text":"My mother was claimed by the war."},{"time":112000,"text":"My brothers and sisters were scattered."},{"time":116000,"text":"And up to now, me and my father"},{"time":118000,"text":"were detached and I still have issues with him."},{"time":123000,"text":"Seeing people die every day,"},{"time":125000,"text":"my mother crying,"},{"time":127000,"text":"it's like I was raised in a violence."},{"time":132000,"text":"And that made me call myself a war child."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137000,"text":"And not only that, when I was eight"},{"time":139000,"text":"I became a child soldier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143000,"text":"I didn't know what was the war for."},{"time":146000,"text":"But one thing I knew"},{"time":148000,"text":"was an image that I saw that stuck in my head."},{"time":151000,"text":"When I went to the training camp I say,"},{"time":154000,"text":"\"I want to kill as many Muslims,"},{"time":156000,"text":"and as many Arabs, as possible.\""},{"time":159000,"text":"The training wasn't easy, but that was the driving force,"},{"time":162000,"text":"because I wanted to revenge for my family."},{"time":165000,"text":"I wanted to revenge for my village."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171000,"text":"Luckily now things have changed"},{"time":173000,"text":"because I came to discover the truth."},{"time":177000,"text":"What was actually killing us wasn't the Muslims,"},{"time":180000,"text":"wasn't the Arabs."},{"time":182000,"text":"It was somebody sitting somewhere manipulating the system,"},{"time":188000,"text":"and using religion to get what they want to get out of us,"},{"time":192000,"text":"which is the oil, the diamond,"},{"time":195000,"text":"the gold and the land."},{"time":199000,"text":"So realizing the truth gave me a position to choose:"},{"time":204000,"text":"should I continue to hate, or let it go?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"So I happened to forgive. Now I sing"},{"time":210000,"text":"music with the Muslims. I dance with them."},{"time":212000,"text":"I even had a movie out called \"War Child,\""},{"time":214000,"text":"funded by Muslim people."},{"time":217000,"text":"So that pain has gone out."},{"time":221000,"text":"But my story is huge."},{"time":223000,"text":"So I'm just going to go into a different step now,"},{"time":227000,"text":"which is easier for me."},{"time":229000,"text":"I'm going to give you poem"},{"time":231000,"text":"called \"Forced to Sin,\""},{"time":235000,"text":"which is from my album \"War Child.\""},{"time":237000,"text":"I talk about my story."},{"time":239000,"text":"One of the journey that I tread"},{"time":241000,"text":"when I was tempted to eat my friend because we had no food"},{"time":244000,"text":"and we were like around 400."},{"time":246000,"text":"And only 16 people survived that journey."},{"time":249000,"text":"So I hope you're going to hear this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251000,"text":"My dreams are like torment."},{"time":255000,"text":"My every moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":257000,"text":"Voices in my brain, of friends that was slain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262000,"text":"Friends like Lual who died by my side,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":264000,"text":"of starvation."},{"time":266000,"text":"In the burning jungle, and the desert plain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271000,"text":"Next was I, but Jesus heard my cry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274000,"text":"As I was tempted to eat the rotten flesh"},{"time":278000,"text":"of my comrade,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":280000,"text":"he gave me comfort."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282000,"text":"We used to raid villages,"},{"time":284000,"text":"stealing chickens, goats and sheeps,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":287000,"text":"anything we could eat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289000,"text":"I knew it was rude, but we needed food."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292000,"text":"And therefore I was forced to sin,"},{"time":295000,"text":"forced to sin to make a living,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":298000,"text":"forced to sin to make a living."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301000,"text":"Sometimes you gotta lose to win."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304000,"text":"Never give up. Never give in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307000,"text":"Left home at the age of seven."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"One year later, live with an AK-47 by my side."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314000,"text":"Slept with one eye open wide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":316000,"text":"Run, duck, play dead and hide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320000,"text":"I've seen my people die like flies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323000,"text":"But I've never seen a dead body,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":325000,"text":"at least one that I've killed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328000,"text":"But still as I wonder, I won't go under."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331000,"text":"Guns barking like lightning and thunder."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334000,"text":"As a child so young and tender,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":337000,"text":"Words I can't forget I still remember."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340000,"text":"I saw sergeant command raising his hand,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":342000,"text":"no retreat, no surrender."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344000,"text":"I carry the banner of the trauma."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"War child, child without a mama,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":350000,"text":"still fighting in the saga."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352000,"text":"Yet as I wage this new war I'm not alone in this drama."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355000,"text":"No sit or stop, as I reach for the top"}]},{"cues":[{"time":358000,"text":"I'm fully dedicated like a patriotic cop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361000,"text":"I'm on a fight, day and night."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364000,"text":"Sometime I do wrong in order to make things right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369000,"text":"It's like I'm living a dream."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371000,"text":"First time I'm feeling like a human being."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374000,"text":"Ah! The children of Darfur."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378000,"text":"Your empty bellies on the telly and now it's you"},{"time":380000,"text":"that I'm fighting for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383000,"text":"Left home."},{"time":385000,"text":"Don't even know the day I'll ever return."}]},{"cues":[{"time":389000,"text":"My country is war-torn."}]},{"cues":[{"time":391000,"text":"Music I used to hear was bombs and fire of guns."}]},{"cues":[{"time":396000,"text":"So many people die that I don't even cry no more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400000,"text":"Ask God question, what am I here for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403000,"text":"And why are my people poor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":405000,"text":"And why, why when the rest of the children were learning how to read and write,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":410000,"text":"I was learning how to fight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":412000,"text":"I ate snails, vultures, rabbits,"},{"time":415000,"text":"snakes, and anything that had life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418000,"text":"I was ready to eat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420000,"text":"I know it's a shame. But who is to be blamed?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":423000,"text":"That's my story shared in the form of a lesson."}]},{"cues":[{"time":426000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":432000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":434000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":440000,"text":"What energized me and kept me going is the music I do."},{"time":444000,"text":"I never saw anybody"},{"time":447000,"text":"to tell my story to them"},{"time":449000,"text":"so they could advise me or do therapy."},{"time":451000,"text":"So the music had been my therapy for me."},{"time":455000,"text":"It's been where I actually see heaven,"},{"time":459000,"text":"where I can be happy,"},{"time":461000,"text":"where I can be a child again, in dances, through music."},{"time":465000,"text":"So one thing I know about music:"},{"time":467000,"text":"music is the only thing that has power"},{"time":470000,"text":"to enter your cell system,"},{"time":472000,"text":"your mind, your heart,"},{"time":475000,"text":"influence your soul and your spirit,"},{"time":477000,"text":"and can even influence the way you live"},{"time":480000,"text":"without even you knowing."},{"time":483000,"text":"Music is the only thing that can"},{"time":485000,"text":"make you want to wake up your bed"},{"time":487000,"text":"and shake your leg,"},{"time":490000,"text":"without even wanting to do it."},{"time":492000,"text":"And so the power music has"},{"time":495000,"text":"I normally compare to the power love"},{"time":498000,"text":"when love doesn't see a color."},{"time":500000,"text":"You know, if you fall in love with a frog, that's it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502000,"text":"One testimony about how I find music"},{"time":504000,"text":"is powerful is when"},{"time":507000,"text":"I was still a soldier back then."},{"time":510000,"text":"I hated the people in the north."},{"time":513000,"text":"But I don't know why I don't hate their music."},{"time":517000,"text":"So we party and dance to their music."},{"time":520000,"text":"And one thing that shocked me is one day"},{"time":522000,"text":"they brought an Arab musician"},{"time":525000,"text":"to come and entertain the soldiers."},{"time":527000,"text":"And I almost broke my leg dancing to his music."},{"time":530000,"text":"But I had this question."},{"time":532000,"text":"So now I'm doing music so I know what the power of music is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":536000,"text":"So what's happening here?"},{"time":538000,"text":"I've been in a painful journey."},{"time":541000,"text":"Today is day number 233"},{"time":544000,"text":"in which I only eat dinner."},{"time":546000,"text":"I don't eat breakfast. No lunch."},{"time":549000,"text":"And I've done a campaign called"},{"time":551000,"text":"Lose to Win."},{"time":553000,"text":"Where I'm losing so that I could win"},{"time":555000,"text":"the battle that I'm fighting now."},{"time":557000,"text":"So my breakfast, my lunch,"},{"time":561000,"text":"I donate it to a charity that I founded"},{"time":563000,"text":"because we want to build a school in Sudan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566000,"text":"And I'm doing this because also"},{"time":569000,"text":"it's a normal thing in my home, people eat one meal a day."},{"time":573000,"text":"Here I am in the West. I choose not to."},{"time":576000,"text":"So in my village now, kids there,"},{"time":578000,"text":"they normally listen to BBC, or any radio,"},{"time":581000,"text":"and they are waiting to know,"},{"time":583000,"text":"the day Emmanuel will eat his breakfast"},{"time":585000,"text":"it means he got the money to build our school."},{"time":587000,"text":"And so I made a commitment. I say,"},{"time":589000,"text":"\"I'm gonna not eat my breakfast.\""},{"time":592000,"text":"I thought I was famous enough that I would raise the money within one month,"},{"time":595000,"text":"but I've been humbled."},{"time":597000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":600000,"text":"So it's taken me 232 days."},{"time":602000,"text":"And I said, \"No stop until we get it.\""},{"time":605000,"text":"And like it's been done on Facebook, MySpace."},{"time":608000,"text":"The people are giving three dollars."},{"time":610000,"text":"The lowest amount we ever got was 20 cents."},{"time":613000,"text":"Somebody donated 20 cents online."},{"time":615000,"text":"I don't know how they did it."},{"time":617000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":618000,"text":"But that moved me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":620000,"text":"And so, the importance of education to me"},{"time":627000,"text":"is what I'm willing to die for."},{"time":629000,"text":"I'm willing to die for this,"},{"time":631000,"text":"because I know what it can do to my people."},{"time":634000,"text":"Education enlighten your brain,"},{"time":636000,"text":"give you so many chances,"},{"time":638000,"text":"and you're able to survive."},{"time":641000,"text":"As a nation we have been crippled."},{"time":643000,"text":"For so many years we have fed on aid."},{"time":645000,"text":"You see a 20-years-old, 30-years-old"},{"time":647000,"text":"families in a refugee camps."},{"time":649000,"text":"They only get the food that drops from the sky, from the U.N."}]},{"cues":[{"time":654000,"text":"So these people,"},{"time":656000,"text":"you're killing a whole generation if you just give them aid."},{"time":660000,"text":"If anybody want to help us"},{"time":663000,"text":"this is what we need."},{"time":665000,"text":"Give us tools. Give the farmers tools."},{"time":668000,"text":"It's rain. Africa is fertile. They can grow the crops."},{"time":672000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":675000,"text":"Invest in education."},{"time":679000,"text":"Education so that we have strong institution"},{"time":683000,"text":"that can create a revolution to change everything."},{"time":685000,"text":"Because we have all those old men"},{"time":688000,"text":"that are creating wars in Africa. They will die soon."},{"time":691000,"text":"But if you invest in education"},{"time":694000,"text":"then we'll be able to change Africa."},{"time":696000,"text":"That's what I'm asking."},{"time":698000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":704000,"text":"So in order to do that,"},{"time":707000,"text":"I founded a charter called Gua Africa,"},{"time":709000,"text":"where we put kids in school."},{"time":712000,"text":"And now we have a couple in university."},{"time":714000,"text":"We have like 40 kids, ex-child soldiers"},{"time":717000,"text":"mixed with anybody that we feel like we want to support."},{"time":720000,"text":"And I said \"I'm going to put it in practice.\""},{"time":723000,"text":"And with the people that are going to follow me and help me do things."},{"time":726000,"text":"That's what I want to do to change,"},{"time":728000,"text":"to make a difference in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":730000,"text":"Well now, my time is going,"},{"time":732000,"text":"so I want to sing a song."},{"time":734000,"text":"But I'll ask you guys to stand up"},{"time":736000,"text":"so we celebrate the life of a British aid worker"},{"time":739000,"text":"called Emma McCune"},{"time":741000,"text":"that made it possible for me to be here."},{"time":744000,"text":"I'm gonna sing this song,"},{"time":747000,"text":"just to inspire you how this woman has made a difference."},{"time":750000,"text":"She came to my country and saw the importance"},{"time":755000,"text":"of education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":757000,"text":"She said the only way to help Sudan"},{"time":759000,"text":"is to invest in the women, educating them,"},{"time":762000,"text":"educating the children,"},{"time":764000,"text":"so that they could come and create a revolution"},{"time":766000,"text":"in this complex society."},{"time":769000,"text":"So she even ended up marrying a commander"},{"time":772000,"text":"from the SPLA."},{"time":775000,"text":"And she rescued over 150 child soldiers."},{"time":778000,"text":"One of them happened to be me now."},{"time":780000,"text":"And so at this moment I want to ask to celebrate Emma with me."},{"time":785000,"text":"Are you guys ready to celebrate Emma?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":787000,"text":"Audience: Yes!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":788000,"text":"Emmanuel Jal: All right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":794000,"text":"♫ This one goes to Emma McCune ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":797000,"text":"♫ Angel to rescue came one afternoon ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":800000,"text":"♫ I'm here because you rescued me ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":803000,"text":"♫ I'm proud to carry your legacy ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":807000,"text":"♫ Thank you. Bless you. R.I.P. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":813000,"text":"♫ What would I be? Me! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":815000,"text":"♫ If Emma never rescued me? What would I be? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":819000,"text":"♫ What would I be? Me! ♫"},{"time":821000,"text":"♫ Another starving refugee ♫"},{"time":823000,"text":"♫ What would I be? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":825000,"text":"♫ What would I be? Me! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":827000,"text":"♫ If Emma never rescued me? Yeah! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":829000,"text":"♫ Yeah! Yeah! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":834000,"text":"♫ You would have seen my face on the telly ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":837000,"text":"♫ Fat hungry belly ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":839000,"text":"♫ Flies in my eyes, head too big for my size ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":842000,"text":"♫ Just another little starving child ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":845000,"text":"♫ Running around in Africa, born to be wild ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":848000,"text":"♫ Praise God, praise the Almighty ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":851000,"text":"♫ for sending an angel to rescue me ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":854000,"text":"♫ I got a reason for being on this Earth ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":857000,"text":"♫ 'Cause I know more than many what a life is worth ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":859000,"text":"♫ Now that I got a chance to stand my ground ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":862000,"text":"♫ I'm gonna run over mountains, leaps and bounds ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":866000,"text":"♫ I ain't an angel, hope I'll be one soon ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":868000,"text":"♫ And if I am, I wanna be like Emma McCune ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":871000,"text":"♫ Me! What would I be? Me! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":875000,"text":"♫ If Emma never rescued me? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":877000,"text":"♫ What would I be? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":879000,"text":"♫ What would I be? Me! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":881000,"text":"♫ Another starving refugee ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":883000,"text":"♫ What would I be? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":885000,"text":"♫ What would I be? Me! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":887000,"text":"♫ If Emma never rescued me? Yeah! Yeah!♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":889000,"text":"♫ Yeah, Yeah! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":895000,"text":"♫ I would have probably died from starvation ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":898000,"text":"♫ Or some other wretched disease ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":902000,"text":"♫ I would have grown up with no education ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":905000,"text":"♫ Just another refugee ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":908000,"text":"♫ I stand here because somebody cared ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":911000,"text":"♫ I stand here because somebody dared ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":914000,"text":"♫ I know there is a lot of Emmas out there ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":916000,"text":"♫ Who is willing and trying to save a life of a child ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":920000,"text":"♫ What would I be? Me! ♫"},{"time":922000,"text":"♫ If Emma never rescued me? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":925000,"text":"♫ What would I be? ♫"},{"time":927000,"text":"♫ What would I be? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":929000,"text":"♫ Another starving refugee ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":931000,"text":"♫ I remember the time when I was small ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":934000,"text":"♫ When I couldn't read or write at all ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":937000,"text":"♫ Now I'm all grown up, I got my education ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":940000,"text":"♫ The sky is the limit and I can't be stopped by no one ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":943000,"text":"♫ How I prayed for this day to come ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":947000,"text":"♫ And I pray that the world find wisdom ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":950000,"text":"♫ To give the poor in need some assistance ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":953000,"text":"♫ Instead of putting up resistance, yeah ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":956000,"text":"♫ Sitting and waiting for the politics to fix this ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":960000,"text":"♫ It ain't gonna happen ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":962000,"text":"♫ They're all sitting on they asses ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":965000,"text":"♫ Popping champagne and sponging off the masses ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":968000,"text":"♫ Coming from a refugee boy-soldier ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":971000,"text":"♫ But I still got my dignity ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":974000,"text":"♫ I gotta say it again ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":976000,"text":"♫ If Emma never rescued me ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":978000,"text":"♫ I'd be a corpse on the African plain ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":981000,"text":"Is there anybody who's here in the back, some love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":984000,"text":"Big scream for Emma everybody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":986000,"text":"Yeah! I'm gonna get crazy now."}]}